 id="aspace_1ef96463771e91987bf0534c05a4099b" level="item"><did><unittitle>N.Y.O. &amp; W. train with Engine No. 68 with two railroad men in front. Undated.</unittitle><container id="aspace_1f445463db5c419c649ebca814cf2458" label="Mixed Materials [31924065254546]" type="manuscript box">80 - Folder 1</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_cbd411fa425bad56f807b77d984e21de" level="item"><did><unittitle>Engine with "Pittston" and L.V.R. on the front. Undated.</unittitle><container id="aspace_bddf7f9ab7b6d5d7d18d5a326341e132" label="Mixed Materials [31924065254546]" type="manuscript box">80 - Folder 1</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_de17f9a4ef4e208f9481f6433f1c7e93" level="item"><did><unittitle>Engine with four men in front and one in the engine. Undated.</unittitle><container id="aspace_b84311c33334434285f1fd97db3edd74" label="Mixed Materials [31924065254546]" type="manuscript box">80 - Folder 1</container></did></c01></dsc>
